high_descs: Move to the counter top to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter top.
Move a few feet to the counter on the right side of the stove.
Cut the heal off the loaf of bread.
Set the knife down on the loaf of bread.
Pick up the heal of the bread.
Turn left and head to the fridge on your right.
Put the heal of bread on the left side of the second shelf in the fridge for a few seconds and then take it back out.
Turn around and move across the room to the microwave above the sink.
Put the bread in the microwave on the left of the apple.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled heal of bread into the microwave.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Step to the right to face the opposite end of the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Place the knife on top of the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from on the table.
Turn left and walk to face the fridge on the right.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and then remove it.
Turn around and walk across the room and face the microwave.
Place the bread slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a bread slice plus store it in the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn right and head to the counter on the right of the stove.
Cut a slice of bread.
Put the knife on the bread.
Pick up the slice of bread.
Turn left and go to the fridge.
Put the bread in the fridge on the second shelf, close the fridge, open the fridge and pick up the slice of bread.
Turn around and head to the microwave above the sink.
Put the bread in the microwave on the left side.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the microwave.
